	(10,1,'2015-03-05 20:59:37','2015-03-05 20:59:37','[vc_row el_class=\"clearfix phil-app phil-app-march\" gmbt_prlx_bg_type=\"parallax\" gmbt_prlx_break_parents=\"0\" gmbt_prlx_smooth_scrolling=\"\" gmbt_prlx_video_youtube_mute=\"\" gmbt_prlx_video_youtube_loop_trigger=\"0\" gmbt_prlx_video_aspect_ratio=\"16:9\" gmbt_prlx_parallax=\"none\" gmbt_prlx_speed=\"0.3\" gmbt_prlx_enable_mobile=\"\"][vc_column width=\"1/1\"][vc_row_inner][vc_column_inner width=\"1/2\" el_class=\"phil-image\"][vc_single_image image=\"106\" border_color=\"grey\" img_link_large=\"\" img_link_target=\"_self\" img_size=\"500x500\"][/vc_column_inner][vc_column_inner width=\"1/2\" el_class=\"phil-text\"][themestudio_title title=\"Philosophy\" align=\"align-center\" text_align=\"center\" title_color=\"#252525\" underline_color=\"#252525\"][/themestudio_title][vc_column_text]\r\n<p style=\"text-align: left;\">I’m not a digital marketer; I’m a marketer with digital expertise. I founded my consultancy because I am fiercely passionate about what I do, and I believe there is tremendous opportunity to succeed across the paid, owned and earned landscape. By marrying the best of emerging tech, strategy, media and marketing, I help organizations develop holistic and integrated strategies, built to evolve as the landscape shifts, to drive current and future goals. <em>The results:</em> laser-focused efforts that drive engagement and ROI.</p>\r\n\r\n[/vc_column_text][/vc_column_inner][/vc_row_inner][vc_row_inner][vc_column_inner width=\"1/2\" el_class=\"phil-text\"][themestudio_title title=\"Approach\" align=\"align-center\" text_align=\"center\" title_color=\"#252525\" underline_color=\"#252525\"][/themestudio_title][vc_column_text]\r\n<p style=\"text-align: left;\">Why Abbot + Water? The name represents my approach – a little bit NYC, a little bit LA. But most importantly, it represents the digital world we’re doing business in. Digital isn’t a NYC thing – it’s an everywhere thing. Digital is my expertise, bicoastal is my beat, and I bring the best of both to everyone I work with.</p>\r\n\r\n[/vc_column_text][/vc_column_inner][vc_column_inner width=\"1/2\" el_class=\"phil-image\"][vc_single_image image=\"112\" border_color=\"grey\" img_link_large=\"\" img_link_target=\"_self\" img_size=\"500x500\"][/vc_column_inner][/vc_row_inner][/vc_column][/vc_row]','Philosophy + Approach','','publish','open','open','','philosophy-approach','','','2015-04-02 14:19:01','2015-04-02 14:19:01','',0,'http://abbot-water.com/?page_id=10',5,'page','',0),
	(11,1,'2015-03-05 20:59:37','2015-03-05 20:59:37','','Philosophy + Approach','','inherit','open','open','','10-revision-v1','','','2015-03-05 20:59:37','2015-03-05 20:59:37','',10,'http://abbot-water.com/2015/03/05/10-revision-v1/',0,'revision','',0),
	(12,1,'2015-03-05 20:59:49','2015-03-05 20:59:49','[vc_row][vc_column][vc_row_inner el_class=\"services-heading\"][vc_column_inner width=\"1/1\" el_class=\"services-march-heading\"][vc_column_text el_class=\"services-march-tagline\"]\r\n<p style=\"text-align: left;\">Abbot + Water sits at the intersection of tech, strategy, media and marketing, from NYC to LA and everywhere in between.</p>\r\nWe work with a broad clientele of brands, publishers, ad tech companies and start-ups as digital marketing experts with a focus on content, video and media.\r\n\r\n[/vc_column_text][/vc_column_inner][/vc_row_inner][/vc_column][/vc_row][vc_row el_class=\"services-sections\" gmbt_prlx_bg_type=\"parallax\" gmbt_prlx_break_parents=\"0\" gmbt_prlx_smooth_scrolling=\"\" gmbt_prlx_video_youtube_mute=\"\" gmbt_prlx_video_youtube_loop_trigger=\"0\" gmbt_prlx_video_aspect_ratio=\"16:9\" gmbt_prlx_parallax=\"none\" gmbt_prlx_speed=\"0.3\" gmbt_prlx_enable_mobile=\"\"][vc_column width=\"1/1\" el_class=\"services-blurb\"][vc_row_inner][vc_column_inner width=\"1/3\"][themestudio_title title=\"Brands\" align=\"align-center\" text_align=\"center\" title_color=\"#252525\" underline_color=\"#252525\"][/themestudio_title][vc_column_text]\r\n<p style=\"text-align: left;\">Consider us your Digital SWAT team. We’ll marry your marketing and digital plans with informed, innovative and results-driven digital strategies, coordinating offline and online content, social marketing, technology, media, and communications across paid, owned and earned channels.</p>\r\n[/vc_column_text][/vc_column_inner][vc_column_inner width=\"1/3\"][themestudio_title title=\"Start-Ups\" align=\"align-center\" text_align=\"center\" title_color=\"#252525\" underline_color=\"#252525\"][/themestudio_title][vc_column_text]\r\n<p style=\"text-align: left;\">Creative and scrappy – our specialty when developing brand strategy and marketing for start-ups. If you have a product, and funding, it’s time to build your brand. We’ll create branding, content and media strategies that complement DR activities, to build targeted awareness and drive revenue.</p>\r\n[/vc_column_text][/vc_column_inner][vc_column_inner width=\"1/3\"][themestudio_title title=\"Publishers / Ad Tech\" align=\"align-center\" text_align=\"center\" title_color=\"#252525\" underline_color=\"#252525\"][/themestudio_title][vc_column_text]\r\n<p style=\"text-align: left;\">Brand-side marketing insight can help you differentiate yourself when fighting for ad dollars. Together we’ll focus on business development efforts to enrich your brand and agency relationships, develop new ad offerings and unlock video, content and native, all with monetization in mind.</p>\r\n[/vc_column_text][/vc_column_inner][/vc_row_inner][/vc_column][/vc_row][vc_row][vc_column width=\"1/1\"][vc_text_separator title=\"SERVICES\" title_align=\"separator_align_center\" align=\"align_center\" color=\"grey\"][/vc_column][/vc_row][vc_row][vc_column width=\"1/1\"][themestudio_service_shortcode posts_per_page=\"8\" has_boder=\"yes\"][/vc_column][/vc_row]','Services','','publish','closed','closed','','services','','','2015-03-19 18:48:36','2015-03-19 18:48:36','',0,'http://abbot-water.com/?page_id=12',4,'page','',0),
