	(29,1,'2015-03-05 21:38:09','2015-03-05 21:38:09','About Heather:\r\n\r\nA results-driven digital brand marketing and media expert, Heather Bergstein has spent over a decade working with global Beauty and Fashion companies including L’Oreal, Ralph Lauren and Estee Lauder. Heather’s career began in traditional marketing, and that remains to be the foundation of her approach; she’s not a digital marketer, but a marketer with digital expertise.\r\n\r\n&nbsp;\r\n\r\nAs President and Chief Strategist of Abbot + Water, Heather works with brands, start-ups and publishers as a dot connector, cross-functional leader, and digital swat team of one, creating tailored and informed strategies that drive engagement and ROI, built to evolve in an ever-changing marketing landscape.\r\n\r\n&nbsp;\r\n\r\nA passionate digital leader, Heather is a frequent panelist and industry participant with a focus on digital content, video and media strategy; her activities, honors awards speak to her dedication. She is based in NYC, where she lives with her son, and bounces between NYC and Santa Monica (aka Silicon Beach), to stay on the pulse of media, tech and everything in between, coast to coast.\r\n\r\n&nbsp;\r\n\r\nActivities, Honors, Awards\r\n<ul>\r\n	<li>Brand Innovators 40 Under 40, Class of 2013</li>\r\n	<li>Editorial Board Member, <em>Journal of Business to Consumer Marketing</em></li>\r\n	<li>Internet Week 2014 Panelist, OMMA Social</li>\r\n	<li>Member, IAB MIXX Screening Committee, 2013 and 2014</li>\r\n	<li>Co-Founder, The Cabernet Group</li>\r\n	<li>Volunteer Content Contributor, Taste of Tribeca</li>\r\n	<li>Upcoming Panelist: Click Z Live NYC 2015</li>\r\n</ul>','Bio + Credentials','','inherit','open','open','','8-revision-v1','','','2015-03-05 21:38:09','2015-03-05 21:38:09','',8,'http://abbot-water.com/2015/03/05/8-revision-v1/',0,'revision','',0),
	(30,1,'2015-03-05 21:46:43','2015-03-05 21:46:43','Philosophy\r\n\r\nI’m not a digital marketer; I’m a marketer with digital expertise. I founded my consultancy because I am fiercely passionate about what I do, and I believe there is tremendous opportunity to succeed across the paid, owned and earned landscape. By marrying the best of emerging tech, strategy, media and marketing, I help organizations develop holistic and integrated strategies, built to evolve as the landscape shifts, to drive current and future goals. The results: laser-focused efforts that drive engagement and ROI.\r\n\r\n&nbsp;\r\n\r\nApproach\r\n\r\nWhy Abbot + Water? The name represents my approach – a little bit NYC, a little bit LA – and it sounds cool. But most importantly, it represents the digital world we’re doing business in. Digital isn’t a NYC thing – it’s an everywhere thing. Digital is my expertise, bicoastal is my beat, and I bring the best of both to everyone I work with.','Philosophy + Approach','','inherit','open','open','','10-revision-v1','','','2015-03-05 21:46:43','2015-03-05 21:46:43','',10,'http://abbot-water.com/2015/03/05/10-revision-v1/',0,'revision','',0),
	(31,1,'2015-03-18 18:07:22','2015-03-18 18:07:22','[vc_row][vc_column width=\"1/1\"][vc_empty_space height=\"15px\"][/vc_column][vc_column][vc_row_inner el_class=\"services-heading\"][vc_column_inner width=\"1/1\"][vc_column_text el_class=\"services-march-tagline\"]\n<p style=\"text-align: left;\">Abbot + Water sits at the intersection of tech, strategy, media and marketing, from NYC to LA and everywhere in between.</p>\nWe work with a broad clientele of brands, publishers, ad tech companies and start-ups as digital marketing experts with a focus on content, video and media.\n\n[/vc_column_text][/vc_column_inner][/vc_row_inner][/vc_column][/vc_row][vc_row el_class=\"services-sections\" gmbt_prlx_bg_type=\"parallax\" gmbt_prlx_break_parents=\"0\" gmbt_prlx_smooth_scrolling=\"\" gmbt_prlx_video_youtube_mute=\"\" gmbt_prlx_video_youtube_loop_trigger=\"0\" gmbt_prlx_video_aspect_ratio=\"16:9\" gmbt_prlx_parallax=\"none\" gmbt_prlx_speed=\"0.3\" gmbt_prlx_enable_mobile=\"\"][vc_column width=\"1/1\" el_class=\"services-blurb\"][vc_row_inner][vc_column_inner width=\"1/3\"][themestudio_title title=\"Brands\" align=\"align-center\" text_align=\"center\" title_color=\"#252525\" underline_color=\"#252525\"][/themestudio_title][vc_column_text]\n<p style=\"text-align: left;\">Consider us your Digital SWAT team. We’ll marry your marketing and digital plans with informed, innovative and results-driven digital strategies, coordinating offline and online content, social marketing, technology, media, and communications across paid, owned and earned channels.</p>\n[/vc_column_text][/vc_column_inner][vc_column_inner width=\"1/3\"][themestudio_title title=\"Start-Ups\" align=\"align-center\" text_align=\"center\" title_color=\"#252525\" underline_color=\"#252525\"][/themestudio_title][vc_column_text]\n<p style=\"text-align: left;\">Creative and scrappy – our specialty when developing brand strategy and marketing for start-ups. If you have a product, and funding, it’s time to build your brand. We’ll create branding, content and media strategies that complement DR activities, to build targeted awareness and drive revenue.</p>\n[/vc_column_text][/vc_column_inner][vc_column_inner width=\"1/3\"][themestudio_title title=\"Publishers / Ad Tech\" align=\"align-center\" text_align=\"center\" title_color=\"#252525\" underline_color=\"#252525\"][/themestudio_title][vc_column_text]\n<p style=\"text-align: left;\">Brand-side marketing insight can help you differentiate yourself when fighting for ad dollars. Together we’ll focus on business development efforts to enrich your brand and agency relationships, develop new ad offerings and unlock video, content and native, all with monetization in mind.</p>\n[/vc_column_text][/vc_column_inner][/vc_row_inner][/vc_column][/vc_row][vc_row el_class=\"space-holder\" gmbt_prlx_bg_type=\"parallax\" gmbt_prlx_break_parents=\"0\" gmbt_prlx_smooth_scrolling=\"\" gmbt_prlx_video_youtube_mute=\"\" gmbt_prlx_video_youtube_loop_trigger=\"0\" gmbt_prlx_video_aspect_ratio=\"16:9\" gmbt_prlx_parallax=\"none\" gmbt_prlx_speed=\"0.3\" gmbt_prlx_enable_mobile=\"\"][vc_column width=\"1/1\"][vc_empty_space height=\"25px\" el_class=\"services-space\"][/vc_column][/vc_row][vc_row][vc_column width=\"1/1\"][vc_text_separator title=\"SERVICES\" title_align=\"separator_align_center\" align=\"align_center\" color=\"grey\"][/vc_column][/vc_row][vc_row][vc_column width=\"1/1\"][themestudio_service_shortcode posts_per_page=\"8\" has_boder=\"yes\"][/vc_column][/vc_row]','Services','','inherit','open','open','','12-autosave-v1','','','2015-03-18 18:07:22','2015-03-18 18:07:22','',12,'http://abbot-water.com/2015/03/05/12-autosave-v1/',0,'revision','',0),
	(32,1,'2015-03-05 21:50:56','2015-03-05 21:50:56','Abbot + Water sits at the intersection of tech, strategy, media and marketing, from NYC to LA and everywhere in between. We work with a broad clientele of brands, publishers, ad tech companies and start-ups as digital marketing experts with a focus on content, video and media.\r\n\r\n&nbsp;\r\n\r\nBrands\r\n\r\nConsider us your Digital SWAT team. We’ll marry your marketing and digital plans with informed, innovative and results-driven digital strategies, proven to be effective across the paid, owned and earned landscape.\r\n\r\n&nbsp;\r\n\r\nPublishers / Ad Tech\r\n\r\nBrand-side marketing insight can help you differentiate yourself when fighting for ad dollars. Together we’ll enrich your brand and agency relationships, develop new ad offerings and unlock video, content and native, with monetization in mind.\r\n\r\n&nbsp;\r\n\r\nStart-ups / Emerging Brands\r\n\r\nCreative and scrappy – our specialty when working with start-ups. If you have a product, and funding, it’s time to build your brand. We’ll create content and media strategies that complement DR activities, to build targeted awareness and drive revenue.\r\n\r\nServices:\r\n<ul>\r\n	<li><span style=\"text-decoration: underline;\">Content Marketing &amp; Distribution</span>:  The lines between brands and publishers have never been blurrier, but the issues are clear – you need eyeballs on the editorial content you are creating. Simply put – I help clients craft strategic marketing and distribution strategies that drive engagement with the content you spend time and money creating, then measure the impact of those efforts to the business with solid KPIs.</li>\r\n	<li><span style=\"text-decoration: underline;\">Video Strategy</span>: How do you navigate a fragmented, cluttered  and messy landscape? With expertise and education. We’ll start with an overview of the video landscape, then move on to tailored navigation of and strategy for video your content and advertising, across devices, platforms and publishers.</li>\r\n	<li><span style=\"text-decoration: underline;\">Brand Building</span>: You’ve got a product, you’ve got funding. Now you need to build a brand, build awareness, and generate revenue. I’ll leverage my billion-dollar-brand marketing experience to develop innovative strategies, materials and content, targeted to your audience, in an efficient and scrappy way, to complement DR marketing and other lower-funnel activities.</li>\r\n	<li><span style=\"text-decoration: underline;\">Media Strategy</span>:  Banners, search, social, video, high-impact, programmatic, mobile – there are many cookie-cutter media plans out there by accident and by design. With a depth of knowledge across online and offline media, I build strategies for effective investment that support, and impact, brand goals.</li>\r\n	<li><span style=\"text-decoration: underline;\">Ad Product Development &amp; Monetization</span>: As a Publisher or Ad Tech Vendor, Brand Marketer attention, and advertising dollars, can be hard to get! I\'ll leverage my +12-year brand-side career to create marketable and differentiated ad products for you, while unlocking new revenue streams around content, video and native. As the recipient of countless pitches, I’ve seen the good, the bad and the ugly. I can help you avoid those last two categories while enriching your selling efforts, creating ROI for brand and agency clients, with monetization in mind.</li>\r\n	<li><span style=\"text-decoration: underline;\">Communications Planning and Social Marketing:</span> At the intersection of PR, Marketing and Influencers, you need synthesized communications and social marketing planning. I’ll help you coordinate across teams, departments and agencies to determine how and where to communicate, with tailored content and a solid amplification plan, both must-haves in the PR and social stratosphere.</li>\r\n	<li><span style=\"text-decoration: underline;\">Innovation and Emerging Tech</span>:  Does your team have a Digital Inspiration Pipeline? How do you operationalize innovation? I curate the emerging tech landscape, providing strategic counsel on relevant trends, while crafting tailored test-and-learn opportunities for brands big and small.</li>\r\n	<li><span style=\"text-decoration: underline;\">Resource Management:</span> How can you get the most out of your resource and agency partners? As a cross-functional leader, I’ve managed teams across agencies, brands and publishers to accomplish projects that can span weeks, months or years. With honed communication skills and detail-focused project management, no team is too big (or too small) to be productive.</li>\r\n</ul>','Services','','inherit','open','open','','12-revision-v1','','','2015-03-05 21:50:56','2015-03-05 21:50:56','',12,'http://abbot-water.com/2015/03/05/12-revision-v1/',0,'revision','',0),
	(33,1,'2015-03-05 21:51:12','2015-03-05 21:51:12','Abbot + Water sits at the intersection of tech, strategy, media and marketing, from NYC to LA and everywhere in between. We work with a broad clientele of brands, publishers, ad tech companies and start-ups as digital marketing experts with a focus on content, video and media.\r\n\r\n&nbsp;\r\n\r\nBrands\r\n\r\nConsider us your Digital SWAT team. We’ll marry your marketing and digital plans with informed, innovative and results-driven digital strategies, proven to be effective across the paid, owned and earned landscape.\r\n\r\n&nbsp;\r\n\r\nPublishers / Ad Tech\r\n\r\nBrand-side marketing insight can help you differentiate yourself when fighting for ad dollars. Together we’ll enrich your brand and agency relationships, develop new ad offerings and unlock video, content and native, with monetization in mind.\r\n\r\n&nbsp;\r\n\r\nStart-ups / Emerging Brands\r\n\r\nCreative and scrappy – our specialty when working with start-ups. If you have a product, and funding, it’s time to build your brand. We’ll create content and media strategies that complement DR activities, to build targeted awareness and drive revenue.\r\n\r\n&nbsp;\r\n\r\nServices:\r\n<ul>\r\n	<li><span style=\"text-decoration: underline;\">Content Marketing &amp; Distribution</span>:  The lines between brands and publishers have never been blurrier, but the issues are clear – you need eyeballs on the editorial content you are creating. Simply put – I help clients craft strategic marketing and distribution strategies that drive engagement with the content you spend time and money creating, then measure the impact of those efforts to the business with solid KPIs.</li>\r\n	<li><span style=\"text-decoration: underline;\">Video Strategy</span>: How do you navigate a fragmented, cluttered  and messy landscape? With expertise and education. We’ll start with an overview of the video landscape, then move on to tailored navigation of and strategy for video your co