brands big and small.</li>\r\n	<li><span style=\"text-decoration: underline;\">Resource Management:</span> How can you get the most out of your resource and agency partners? As a cross-functional leader, I’ve managed teams across agencies, brands and publishers to accomplish projects that can span weeks, months or years. With honed communication skills and detail-focused project management, no team is too big (or too small) to be productive.</li>\r\n</ul>[/vc_column_text][/vc_column][vc_column][themestudio_service_shortcode posts_per_page=\"8\" css_class=\"Service\" has_boder=\"no\"][/vc_column][/vc_row]','Services','','inherit','open','open','','12-revision-v1','','','2015-03-06 18:36:22','2015-03-06 18:36:22','',12,'http://abbot-water.com/2015/03/06/12-revision-v1/',0,'revision','',0),
