	(75,1,'2015-03-09 20:35:16','2015-03-09 20:35:16','[vc_row][vc_column width=\"1/1\"][themestudio_title title=\"Heather Bergstein\" align=\"align-center\" text_align=\"center\" title_color=\"#252525\" underline_color=\"#252525\"]President | Chief Strategist[/themestudio_title][/vc_column][/vc_row][vc_row][vc_column width=\"1/1\"][vc_single_image image=\"34\" border_color=\"grey\" img_link_large=\"\" img_link_target=\"_self\" img_size=\"500x667\" alignment=\"center\"][/vc_column][/vc_row][vc_row][vc_column width=\"1/1\"][vc_column_text]A results-driven digital brand marketing and media expert, Heather Bergstein has spent over a decade working with global Beauty and Fashion companies including L’Oreal, Ralph Lauren and Estee Lauder. Heather’s career began in traditional marketing, and that remains to be the foundation of her approach; she’s not a digital marketer, but a marketer with digital expertise.\r\n\r\nAs President and Chief Strategist of Abbot + Water, Heather works with brands, start-ups and publishers as a dot connector, cross-functional leader, and digital swat team of one, creating tailored and informed strategies that drive engagement and ROI, built to evolve in an ever-changing marketing landscape.\r\n\r\nA passionate digital leader, Heather is a frequent panelist and industry participant with a focus on digital content, video and media strategy; her activities, honors awards speak to her dedication. She is based in NYC, where she lives with her son, and bounces between NYC and Santa Monica (aka Silicon Beach), to stay on the pulse of media, tech and everything in between, coast to coast.\r\n[/vc_column_text][/vc_column][/vc_row][vc_row][vc_column width=\"1/1\"][themestudio_title title=\"Activities, Honors + Awards\" align=\"align-center\" text_align=\"center\" title_color=\"#252525\" underline_color=\"#252525\"][/themestudio_title][/vc_column][/vc_row][vc_row][vc_column width=\"1/1\"][vc_column_text]\r\n<p style=\"text-align: center;\">• Brand Innovators 40 Under 40, Class of 2013\r\n• Editorial Board Member, Journal of Business to Consumer Marketing\r\n• Internet Week 2014 Panelist, OMMA Social\r\n• Member, IAB MIXX Screening Committee, 2013 and 2014\r\n• Co-Founder, The Cabernet Group\r\n• Volunteer Content Contributor, Taste of Tribeca\r\n• Upcoming Panelist: Click Z Live NYC 2015\r\n\r\n[/vc_column_text][/vc_column][/vc_row]','Bio + Credentials','','inherit','open','open','','8-revision-v1','','','2015-03-09 20:35:16','2015-03-09 20:35:16','',8,'http://abbot-water.com/?p=75',0,'revision','',0),
	(76,1,'2015-03-09 21:19:04','2015-03-09 21:19:04','[vc_row][vc_column width=\"1/1\"][vc_column_text]\r\n<p style=\"text-align: center;\">Abbot + Water sits at the intersection of tech, strategy, media and marketing, from NYC to LA and everywhere in between. We work with a broad clientele of brands, publishers, ad tech companies and start-ups as digital marketing experts with a focus on content, video and media.</p>\r\n[/vc_column_text][/vc_column][/vc_row][vc_row][vc_column width=\"1/1\"][themestudio_title title=\"Brands\" align=\"align-center\" text_align=\"center\" title_color=\"#252525\" underline_color=\"#252525\"][/themestudio_title][/vc_column][/vc_row][vc_row][vc_column width=\"1/1\"][vc_column_text]\r\n<p style=\"text-align: center;\">Consider us your Digital SWAT team. We’ll marry your marketing and digital plans with informed, innovative and results-driven digital strategies, proven to be effective across the paid, owned and earned landscape.</p>\r\n[/vc_column_text][/vc_column][/vc_row][vc_row][vc_column width=\"1/1\"][themestudio_title title=\"Publishers / Ad Tech\" align=\"align-center\" text_align=\"center\" title_color=\"#252525\" underline_color=\"#252525\"][/themestudio_title][/vc_column][/vc_row][vc_row][vc_column width=\"1/1\"][vc_column_text]\r\n<p style=\"text-align: center;\">Brand-side marketing insight can help you differentiate yourself when fighting for ad dollars. Together we’ll enrich your brand and agency relationships, develop new ad offerings and unlock video, content and native, with monetization in mind.</p>\r\n[/vc_column_text][/vc_column][/vc_row][vc_row][vc_column width=\"1/1\"][themestudio_title title=\"Start-Ups / Emerging Brands\" align=\"align-center\" text_align=\"center\" title_color=\"#252525\" underline_color=\"#252525\"][/themestudio_title][/vc_column][/vc_row][vc_row][vc_column width=\"1/1\"][vc_column_text]\r\n<p style=\"text-align: center;\">Creative and scrappy – our specialty when working with start-ups. If you have a product, and funding, it’s time to build your brand. We’ll create content and media strategies that complement DR activities, to build targeted awareness and drive revenue.</p>\r\n[/vc_column_text][/vc_column][/vc_row]','Services','','inherit','open','open','','12-revision-v1','','','2015-03-09 21:19:04','2015-03-09 21:19:04','',12,'http://abbot-water.com/2015/03/09/12-revision-v1/',0,'revision','',0),
	(77,1,'2015-03-09 21:54:05','2015-03-09 21:54:05','[vc_row][vc_column width=\"1/1\"][vc_column_text]\r\n<p style=\"text-align: center;\">Abbot + Water sits at the intersection of tech, strategy, media and marketing, from NYC to LA and everywhere in between. We work with a broad clientele of brands, publishers, ad tech companies and start-ups as digital marketing experts with a focus on content, video and media.</p>\r\n\r\n[/vc_column_text][/vc_column][/vc_row][vc_row][vc_column width=\"1/1\"][themestudio_title title=\"Brands\" align=\"align-center\" text_align=\"center\" title_color=\"#252525\" underline_color=\"#252525\"][/themestudio_title][/vc_column][/vc_row][vc_row][vc_column width=\"1/1\"][vc_column_text]\r\n<p style=\"text-align: center;\">Consider us your Digital SWAT team. We’ll marry your marketing and digital plans with informed, innovative and results-driven digital strategies, proven to be effective across the paid, owned and earned landscape.</p>\r\n\r\n[/vc_column_text][/vc_column][/vc_row][vc_row][vc_column width=\"1/1\"][themestudio_title title=\"Publishers / Ad Tech\" align=\"align-center\" text_align=\"center\" title_color=\"#252525\" underline_color=\"#252525\"][/themestudio_title][/vc_column][/vc_row][vc_row][vc_column width=\"1/1\"][vc_column_text]\r\n<p style=\"text-align: center;\">Brand-side marketing insight can help you differentiate yourself when fighting for ad dollars. Together we’ll enrich your brand and agency relationships, develop new ad offerings and unlock video, content and native, with monetization in mind.</p>\r\n\r\n[/vc_column_text][/vc_column][/vc_row][vc_row][vc_column width=\"1/1\"][themestudio_title title=\"Start-Ups / Emerging Brands\" align=\"align-center\" text_align=\"center\" title_color=\"#252525\" underline_color=\"#252525\"][/themestudio_title][/vc_column][/vc_row][vc_row][vc_column width=\"1/1\"][vc_column_text]\r\n<p style=\"text-align: center;\">Creative and scrappy – our specialty when working with start-ups. If you have a product, and funding, it’s time to build your brand. We’ll create content and media strategies that complement DR activities, to build targeted awareness and drive revenue.</p>\r\n\r\n[/vc_column_text][/vc_column][/vc_row][vc_row][vc_column width=\"1/1\"][themestudio_service_shortcode posts_per_page=\"5\" has_boder=\"no\"][/vc_column][/vc_row]','Services','','inherit','open','open','','12-revision-v1','','','2015-03-09 21:54:05','2015-03-09 21:54:05','',12,'http://abbot-water.com/2015/03/09/12-revision-v1/',0,'revision','',0),
	(78,1,'2015-03-09 21:55:48','2015-03-09 21:55:48','[vc_row][vc_column width=\"1/2\"][themestudio_title title=\"Philosophy\" align=\"align-center\" text_align=\"center\" title_color=\"#252525\" underline_color=\"#252525\"][/themestudio_title][/vc_column][/vc_row][vc_row][vc_column width=\"1/2\"][vc_column_text]\r\n<p style=\"text-align: center;\">I’m not a digital marketer; I’m a marketer with digital expertise. I founded my consultancy because I am fiercely passionate about what I do, and I believe there is tremendous opportunity to succeed across the paid, owned and earned landscape. By marrying the best of emerging tech, strategy, media and marketing, I help organizations develop holistic and integrated strategies, built to evolve as the landscape shifts, to drive current and future goals. The results: laser-focused efforts that drive engagement and ROI.</p>\r\n\r\n[/vc_column_text][/vc_column][/vc_row][vc_row][vc_column width=\"1/2\"][themestudio_title title=\"Approach\" align=\"align-center\" text_align=\"center\" title_color=\"#252525\" underline_color=\"#252525\"][/themestudio_title][/vc_column][/vc_row][vc_row][vc_column width=\"1/2\"][vc_column_text]\r\n<p style=\"text-align: center;\"><strong>Why Abbot + Water?</strong> The name represents my approach – a little bit NYC, a little bit LA – and it sounds cool. But most importantly, it represents the digital world we’re doing business in. Digital isn’t a NYC thing – it’s an everywhere thing. Digital is my expertise, bicoastal is my beat, and I bring the best of both to everyone I work with.</p>\r\n\r\n[/vc_column_text][/vc_column][/vc_row]','Philosophy + Approach','','inherit','open','open','','10-revision-v1','','','2015-03-09 21:55:48','2015-03-09 21:55:48','',10,'http://abbot-water.com/2015/03/09/10-revision-v1/',0,'revision','',0),
	(80,1,'2015-03-10 14:58:37','2015-03-10 14:58:37','[vc_row][vc_column width=\"1/1\"][themestudio_title title=\"Philosophy\" align=\"align-center\" text_align=\"center\" title_color=\"#252525\" underline_color=\"#252525\"][/themestudio_title][/vc_column][/vc_row][vc_row][vc_column width=\"1/1\"][vc_column_text]\r\n<p style=\"text-align: center;\">I’m not a digital marketer; I’m a marketer with digital expertise. I founded my consultancy because I am fiercely passionate about what I do, and I believe there is tremendous opportunity to succeed across the paid, owned and earned landscape. By marrying the best of emerging tech, strategy, media and marketing, I help organizations develop holistic and integrated strategies, built to evolve as the landscape shifts, to drive current and future goals. The results: laser-focused efforts that drive engagement and ROI.</p>\r\n\r\n[/vc_column_text][/vc_column][/vc_row][vc_row][vc_column width=\"1/1\"][themestudio_title title=\"Approach\" align=\"align-center\" text_align=\"center\" title_color=\"#252525\" underline_color=\"#252525\"][/themestudio_title][/vc_column][/vc_row][vc_row][vc_column width=\"1/1\"][vc_column_text]\r\n<p style=\"text-align: center;\"><strong>Why Abbot + Water?</strong> The name represents my approach – a little bit NYC, a little bit LA – and it sounds cool. But most importantly, it represents the digital world we’re doing business in. Digital isn’t a NYC thing – it’s an everywhere thing. Digital is my expertise, bicoastal is my beat, and I bring the best of both to everyone I work with.</p>\r\n\r\n[/vc_column_text][/vc_column][/vc_row]','Philosophy + Approach','','inherit','open','open','','10-revision-v1','','','2015-03-10 14:58:37','2015-03-10 14:58:37','',10,'http://abbot-water.com/?p=80',0,'revision','',0),
	(81,1,'2015-03-10 14:58:51','2015-03-10 14:58:51','','logo-black','','inherit','open','open','','logo-black-2','','','2015-03-10 14:58:51','2015-03-10 14:58:51','',0,'http://abbot-water.com/wp-content/uploads/2015/03/logo-black1.png',0,'attachment','image/png',0),
	(82,1,'2015-03-10 15:12:43','2015-03-10 15:12:43','[vc_row][vc_column width=\"1/1\"][vc_empty_space height=\"60px\"][/vc_column][/vc_row][vc_row][vc_column width=\"1/2\"][themestudio_title title=\"Philosophy\" align=\"align-center\" text_align=\"center\" title_color=\"#252525\" underline_color=\"#252525\"][/themestudio_title][vc_column_text]\r\n<p style=\"text-align: center;\">I’m not a digital marketer; I’m a marketer with digital expertise. I founded my consultancy because I am fiercely passionate about what I do, and I believe there is tremendous opportunity to succeed across the paid, owned and earned landscape. By marrying the best of emerging tech, strategy, media and marketing, I help organizations develop holistic and integrated strategies, built to evolve as the landscape shifts, to drive current and future goals.</p>\r\n<p style=\"text-align: center;\"><em>The results:</em> laser-focused efforts that drive engagement and ROI.</p>\r\n[/vc_column_text][/vc_column][vc_column width=\"1/2\"][themestudio_title title=\"Approach\" align=\"align-center\" text_align=\"center\" title_color=\"#252525\" underline_color=\"#252525\"][/themestudio_title][vc_column_text]\r\n<p style=\"text-align: center;\"><strong>Why Abbot + Water?</strong> The name represents my approach – a little bit NYC, a little bit LA – and it sounds cool. But most importantly, it represents the digital world we’re doing business in. Digital isn’t a NYC thing – it’s an everywhere thing. Digital is my expertise, bicoastal is my beat, and I bring the best of both to everyone I work with.</p>\r\n[/vc_column_text][/vc_column][/vc_row][vc_row][vc_column width=\"1/1\"][vc_empty_space height=\"60px\"][/vc_column][/vc_row]','Philosophy + Approach','','inherit','open','open','','10-revision-v1','','','2015-03-10 15:12:43','2015-03-10 15:12:43','',10,'http://abbot-water.com/?p=82',0,'revision','',0),
