	(174,1,'2015-03-11 18:07:46','2015-03-11 18:07:46','[vc_row][vc_column width=\"1/1\"][vc_empty_space height=\"60px\"][/vc_column][/vc_row][vc_row][vc_column width=\"1/2\"][themestudio_title title=\"Philosophy\" align=\"align-center\" text_align=\"center\" title_color=\"#252525\" underline_color=\"#252525\"][/themestudio_title][vc_column_text]\r\n<p style=\"text-align: left;\">I’m not a digital marketer; I’m a marketer with digital expertise. I founded my consultancy because I am fiercely passionate about what I do, and I believe there is tremendous opportunity to succeed across the paid, owned and earned landscape. By marrying the best of emerging tech, strategy, media and marketing, I help organizations develop holistic and integrated strategies, built to evolve as the landscape shifts, to drive current and future goals.</p>\r\n<p style=\"text-align: left;\"><em>The results:</em> laser-focused efforts that drive engagement and ROI.</p>\r\n[/vc_column_text][/vc_column][vc_column width=\"1/2\"][themestudio_title title=\"Approach\" align=\"align-center\" text_align=\"center\" title_color=\"#252525\" underline_color=\"#252525\"][/themestudio_title][vc_column_text]\r\n<p style=\"text-align: left;\">Why Abbot + Water?</p>\r\n<p style=\"text-align: left;\">The name represents my approach – a little bit NYC, a little bit LA – and it sounds cool. But most importantly, it represents the digital world we’re doing business in. Digital isn’t a NYC thing – it’s an everywhere thing. Digital is my expertise, bicoastal is my beat, and I bring the best of both to everyone I work with.</p>\r\n[/vc_column_text][/vc_column][/vc_row][vc_row][vc_column width=\"1/1\"][vc_empty_space height=\"60px\"][/vc_column][/vc_row]','Philosophy + Approach','','inherit','open','open','','10-revision-v1','','','2015-03-11 18:07:46','2015-03-11 18:07:46','',10,'http://abbot-water.com/?p=174',0,'revision','',0),
	(175,1,'2015-03-11 18:10:12','2015-03-11 18:10:12','[vc_row][vc_column width=\"1/1\"][vc_empty_space height=\"20px\"][/vc_column][/vc_row][vc_row gmbt_prlx_bg_type=\"parallax\" gmbt_prlx_break_parents=\"0\" gmbt_prlx_smooth_scrolling=\"\" gmbt_prlx_video_youtube_mute=\"\" gmbt_prlx_video_youtube_loop_trigger=\"0\" gmbt_prlx_video_aspect_ratio=\"16:9\" gmbt_prlx_parallax=\"none\" gmbt_prlx_speed=\"0.3\" gmbt_prlx_enable_mobile=\"\"][vc_column width=\"1/2\"][vc_single_image image=\"34\" alignment=\"center\" border_color=\"black\" img_link_large=\"\" img_link_target=\"_self\" img_size=\"500x667\" style=\"vc_box_border\"][/vc_column][vc_column width=\"1/2\"][themestudio_title title=\"Heather Bergstein\" align=\"align-center\" text_align=\"center\" title_color=\"#252525\" underline_color=\"#252525\"]President + Chief Strategist[/themestudio_title][vc_column_text]\r\n<p style=\"text-align: left;\">A results-driven digital brand marketing and media expert, Heather Bergstein has spent over a decade working with global Beauty and Fashion companies including L’Oreal, Ralph Lauren and Estee Lauder. Heather’s career began in traditional marketing, and that remains to be the foundation of her approach; she’s not a digital marketer, but a marketer with digital expertise.</p>\r\n<p style=\"text-align: left;\">As President and Chief Strategist of <strong>Abbot + Water</strong>, Heather works with brands, start-ups and publishers as a dot connector, cross-functional leader, and digital swat team of one, creating tailored and informed strategies that drive engagement and ROI, built to evolve in an ever-changing marketing landscape.</p>\r\n<p style=\"text-align: left;\">A passionate digital leader, Heather is a frequent panelist and industry participant with a focus on digital content, video and media strategy; her activities, honors awards speak to her dedication. She is based in NYC, where she lives with her son, and bounces between NYC and Santa Monica (aka Silicon Beach), to stay on the pulse of media, tech and everything in between, coast to coast.</p>\r\n[/vc_column_text][/vc_column][/vc_row][vc_row][vc_column width=\"1/1\"][themestudio_title title=\"Activities, Honors + Awards\" align=\"align-center\" text_align=\"center\" title_color=\"#252525\" underline_color=\"#252525\"][/themestudio_title][/vc_column][/vc_row][vc_row][vc_column width=\"1/1\"][vc_column_text]\r\n<p style=\"text-align: left;\">Brand Innovators 40 Under 40, Class of 2013\r\nEditorial Board Member,<em> Journal of Business to Consumer Marketing</em>\r\nInternet Week 2014 Panelist, OMMA Social\r\nMember, IAB MIXX Screening Committee, 2013 and 2014\r\nCo-Founder, The Cabernet Group\r\nVolunteer Content Contributor, Taste of Tribeca\r\nUpcoming Panelist: Click Z Live NYC 2015</p>\r\n[/vc_column_text][/vc_column][/vc_row]','Bio + Credentials','','inherit','open','open','','8-revision-v1','','','2015-03-11 18:10:12','2015-03-11 18:10:12','',8,'http://abbot-water.com/?p=175',0,'revision','',0),
