 on the pulse of media, tech and everything in between, coast to coast.</p>\r\n[/vc_column_text][/vc_column][/vc_row][vc_row gmbt_prlx_bg_type=\"parallax\" gmbt_prlx_break_parents=\"0\" gmbt_prlx_smooth_scrolling=\"\" gmbt_prlx_video_youtube_mute=\"\" gmbt_prlx_video_youtube_loop_trigger=\"0\" gmbt_prlx_video_aspect_ratio=\"16:9\" gmbt_prlx_parallax=\"none\" gmbt_prlx_speed=\"0.3\" gmbt_prlx_enable_mobile=\"\"][vc_column width=\"1/2\"][vc_single_image image=\"34\" alignment=\"center\" border_color=\"black\" img_link_large=\"\" img_link_target=\"_self\" img_size=\"500x667\" style=\"vc_box_border\"][/vc_column][vc_column width=\"1/2\"][themestudio_title title=\"Activities, Honors + Awards\" align=\"align-center\" text_align=\"center\" title_color=\"#252525\" underline_color=\"#252525\"][/themestudio_title][vc_column_text]Brand Innovators 40 Under 40, Class of 2013\r\nEditorial Board Member,<em> Journal of Business to Consumer Marketing</em>\r\nInternet Week 2014 Panelist, OMMA Social\r\nMember, IAB MIXX Screening Committee, 2013 and 2014\r\nCo-Founder, The Cabernet Group\r\nVolunteer Content Contributor, Taste of Tribeca\r\nUpcoming Panelist: Click Z Live NYC 2015[/vc_column_text][/vc_column][/vc_row][vc_row][vc_column width=\"1/1\"][themestudio_title title=\"Activities, Honors + Awards\" align=\"align-center\" text_align=\"center\" title_color=\"#252525\" underline_color=\"#252525\"][/themestudio_title][/vc_column][/vc_row][vc_row][vc_column width=\"1/1\"][vc_column_text]\r\n\r\n<p style=\"text-align: left;\">Brand Innovators 40 Under 40, Class of 2013\r\nEditorial Board Member,<em> Journal of Business to Consumer Marketing</em>\r\nInternet Week 2014 Panelist, OMMA Social\r\nMember, IAB MIXX Screening Committee, 2013 and 2014\r\nCo-Founder, The Cabernet Group\r\nVolunteer Content Contributor, Taste of Tribeca\r\nUpcoming Panelist: Click Z Live NYC 2015\r\n\r\n[/vc_column_text][/vc_column][/vc_row]','Bio + Credentials','','inherit','open','open','','8-revision-v1','',