 on the pulse of media, tech and everything in between, coast to coast.</p>\r\n[/vc_column_text][themestudio_title title=\"Activities, Honors + Awards\" align=\"align-center\" text_align=\"center\" title_color=\"#252525\" underline_color=\"#252525\"][/themestudio_title][vc_column_text]Brand Innovators 40 Under 40, Class of 2013\r\nEditorial Board Member,<em> Journal of Business to Consumer Marketing</em>\r\nInternet Week 2014 Panelist, OMMA Social\r\nMember, IAB MIXX Screening Committee, 2013 and 2014\r\nCo-Founder, The Cabernet Group\r\nVolunteer Content Contributor, Taste of Tribeca\r\nUpcoming Panelist: Click Z Live NYC 2015[/vc_column_text][/vc_column][/vc_row]','Bio + Credentials','','inherit','open','open','','8-revision-v1','','','2015-03-11 18:16:44','2015-03-11 18:16:44','',8,'http://abbot-water.com/?p=178',0,'revision','',0),
	(179,1,'2015-03-11 19:05:29','2015-03-11 19:05:29','[vc_row full_width=\"stretch_row\" gmbt_prlx_bg_type=\"parallax\" gmbt_prlx_break_parents=\"0\" gmbt_prlx_smooth_scrolling=\"\" gmbt_prlx_video_youtube_mute=\"\" gmbt_prlx_video_youtube_loop_trigger=\"0\" gmbt_prlx_video_aspect_ratio=\"16:9\" gmbt_prlx_parallax=\"none\" gmbt_prlx_speed=\"0.3\" gmbt_prlx_enable_mobile=\"\"][vc_column width=\"1/1\" css=\".vc_custom_1426006114136{background-image: url(http://abbot-water.com/wp-content/uploads/2015/03/asfalt_@2X.png?id=83) !important;}\"][themestudio_slider_parallax style_parallax=\"image\" video_url=\"http://www.youtube.com/watch?v=-VL_G4SNaGM\" intro_text=\"Digital Strategy &amp; Innovation, Coast to Coast\" images_logo=\"130\" animation_parallax=\"slide\" direction_parallax=\"vertical\" next_section=\"#history\" list_categories=\"Branding\r\n	              				Development\r\n	              				Product\r\n	              				Advertising\"][/themestudio_slider_parallax][/vc_column][/vc_row][vc_row][vc_column width=\"1/1\"][ts_portfolio portfolio_item_width=\"474\" portfolio_item_height=\"350\" portfolio_hover_opacity=\"0.85\" portfolio_single_loading=\"ajax\" portfolio_filter_switch=\"hide-filter\"][/vc_column][/vc_row]','Home','','inherit','open','open','','5-revision-v1','','','2015-03-11 19:05:29','2015-03-11 19:05:29','',5,'http://abbot-water.com/?p=179',0,'revision','',0),
	(180,1,'2015-03-11 20:16:58','2015-03-11 20:16:58','[vc_row][vc_column width=\"1/1\"][vc_empty_space height=\"15px\"][/vc_column][/vc_row][vc_row][vc_column width=\"1/2\"][vc_column_text]\r\n<h3 style=\"text-align: center;\">Abbot + Water sits at the intersection of tech, strategy, media and marketing, from NYC to LA and everywhere in between. We work with a broad clientele of brands, publishers, ad tech companies and start-ups as digital marketing experts with a focus on content, video and media.</h3>\r\n[/vc_column_text][/vc_column][vc_column width=\"1/2\"][themestudio_title title=\"Brands\" align=\"align-center\" text_align=\"center\" title_color=\"#252525\" underline_color=\"#252525\"][/themestudio_title][vc_column_text]\r\n<p style=\"text-align: left;\">Consider us your Digital SWAT team. We’ll marry your marketing and digital plans with informed, innovative and results-driven digital strategies, proven to be effective across the paid, owned and earned landscape.</p>\r\n[/vc_column_text][themestudio_title title=\"Publishers / Ad Tech\" align=\"align-center\" text_align=\"center\" title_color=\"#252525\" underline_color=\"#252525\"][/themestudio_title][vc_column_text]\r\n<p style=\"text-align: left;\">Brand-side marketing insight can help you differentiate yourself when fighting for ad dollars. Together we’ll enrich your brand and agency relationships, develop new ad offerings and unlock video, content and native, with monetization in mind.</p>\r\n[/vc_column_text][themestudio_title title=\"Start-ups / Emerging Brands\" align=\"align-center\" text_align=\"center\" title_color=\"#252525\" underline_color=\"#252525\"][/themestudio_title][vc_column_text]\r\n<p style=\"text-align: left;\">Creative and scrappy – our specialty when working with start-ups. If you have a product, and funding, it’s time to build your brand. We’ll create content and media strategies that complement DR activities, to build targeted awareness and drive revenue.</p>\r\n[/vc_column_text][/vc_column][/vc_row][vc_row][vc_column width=\"1/1\"][vc_empty_space height=\"10px\"][/vc_column][/vc_row][vc_row][vc_column width=\"1/3\"][themestudio_title title=\"Brands\" align=\"align-center\" text_align=\"center\" title_color=\"#252525\" underline_color=\"#252525\"][/themestudio_title][vc_column_text]\r\n<p style=\"text-align: center;\">Consider us your Digital SWAT team. We’ll marry your marketing and digital plans with informed, innovative and results-driven digital strategies, proven to be effective across the paid, owned and earned landscape.</p>\r\n[/vc_column_text][/vc_column][vc_column width=\"1/3\"][themestudio_title title=\"Publishers / Ad Tech\" align=\"align-center\" text_align=\"center\" title_color=\"#252525\" underline_color=\"#252525\"][/themestudio_title][vc_column_text]\r\n<p style=\"text-align: center;\">Brand-side marketing insight can help you differentiate yourself when fighting for ad dollars. Together we’ll enrich your brand and agency relationships, develop new ad offerings and unlock video, content and native, with monetization in mind.</p>\r\n[/vc_column_text][/vc_column][vc_column width=\"1/3\"][themestudio_title title=\"Start-Ups / Emerging Brands\" align=\"align-center\" text_align=\"center\" title_color=\"#252525\" underline_color=\"#252525\"][/themestudio_title][vc_column_text]\r\n<p style=\"text-align: center;\">Creative and scrappy – our specialty when working with start-ups. If you have a product, and funding, it’s time to build your brand. We’ll create content and media strategies that complement DR activities, to build targeted awareness and drive revenue.</p>\r\n[/vc_column_text][/vc_column][/vc_row][vc_row][vc_column width=\"1/1\"][vc_empty_space height=\"32px\"][/vc_column][/vc_row][vc_row][vc_column width=\"1/1\"][vc_text_separator title=\"SERVICES\" title_align=\"separator_align_center\" align=\"align_center\" color=\"grey\"][/vc_column][/vc_row][vc_row gmbt_prlx_bg_type=\"parallax\" gmbt_prlx_break_parents=\"0\" gmbt_prlx