	(185,1,'2015-03-18 18:59:21','2015-03-18 18:59:21','[vc_row][vc_column width=\"1/1\"][vc_empty_space height=\"60px\"][/vc_column][/vc_row][vc_row el_class=\"clearfix phil-app phil-app-march\" gmbt_prlx_bg_type=\"parallax\" gmbt_prlx_break_parents=\"0\" gmbt_prlx_smooth_scrolling=\"\" gmbt_prlx_video_youtube_mute=\"\" gmbt_prlx_video_youtube_loop_trigger=\"0\" gmbt_prlx_video_aspect_ratio=\"16:9\" gmbt_prlx_parallax=\"none\" gmbt_prlx_speed=\"0.3\" gmbt_prlx_enable_mobile=\"\"][vc_column width=\"1/1\"][vc_row_inner][vc_column_inner width=\"1/2\" el_class=\"phil-image\"][vc_single_image image=\"106\" border_color=\"grey\" img_link_large=\"\" img_link_target=\"_self\" img_size=\"500x500\"][/vc_column_inner][vc_column_inner width=\"1/2\" el_class=\"phil-text\"][themestudio_title title=\"Philosophy\" align=\"align-center\" text_align=\"center\" title_color=\"#252525\" underline_color=\"#252525\"][/themestudio_title][vc_column_text]\n<p style=\"text-align: left;\">I’m not a digital marketer; I’m a marketer with digital expertise. I founded my consultancy because I am fiercely passionate about what I do, and I believe there is tremendous opportunity to succeed across the paid, owned and earned landscape. By marrying the best of emerging tech, strategy, media and marketing, I help organizations develop holistic and integrated strategies, built to evolve as the landscape shifts, to drive current and future goals.</p>\n<p style=\"text-align: left;\"><em>The results:</em> laser-focused efforts that drive engagement and ROI.</p>\n[/vc_column_text][/vc_column_inner][/vc_row_inner][vc_row_inner][vc_column_inner width=\"1/2\" el_class=\"phil-text\"][themestudio_title title=\"Approach\" align=\"align-center\" text_align=\"center\" title_color=\"#252525\" underline_color=\"#252525\"][/themestudio_title][vc_column_text]\n<p style=\"text-align: left;\">Why Abbot + Water? The name represents my approach – a little bit NYC, a little bit LA. But most importantly, it represents the digital world we’re doing business in. Digital isn’t a NYC thing – it’s an everywhere thing. Digital is my expertise, bicoastal is my beat, and I bring the best of both to everyone I work with.</p>\n[/vc_column_text][/vc_column_inner][vc_column_inner width=\"1/2\"][vc_single_image image=\"112\" border_color=\"grey\" img_link_large=\"\" img_link_target=\"_self\" img_size=\"500x500\"][/vc_column_inner][/vc_row_inner][/vc_column][/vc_row]','Philosophy + Approach','','inherit','open','open','','10-autosave-v1','','','2015-03-18 18:59:21','2015-03-18 18:59:21','',10,'http://abbot-water.com/?p=185',0,'revision','',0),
