	(211,1,'2015-03-12 13:36:03','2015-03-12 13:36:03','As a Publisher or Ad Tech Vendor, Brand Marketer attention, and advertising dollars, can be hard to get. I\'ll leverage my +12-year brand-side career to co-create marketable and differentiated ad products with you, while unlocking new revenue streams around content, video and native. As the recipient of countless pitches, I’ve seen the good, the bad and the ugly.  avoid those last two categories while enriching your selling efforts, creating ROI for brand and agency clients, with monetization in mind.','Business Development + Monetization','','inherit','open','open','','90-autosave-v1','','','2015-03-12 13:36:03','2015-03-12 13:36:03','',90,'http://abbot-water.com/?p=211',0,'revision','',0),
