t his book <a href=\"http://unconsciousbranding.com/\">here</a>.\r\n\r\n<strong>Day 3 Party: Dropbox </strong>With lots of competing parties, where to go/ Dropbox at <a href=\"http://shop.mellowjohnnys.com/?gclid=CIiAle7Wr8QCFQ8waQodon4ALw\">Mellow Johnny\'s Bike Shop</a>, of course! Great party, and a great 90\'s cover band, Angry Flannel (which founder Drew Houston is a member of). Nirvana, Jane\'s Addiction, represented!\r\n\r\n<strong>Roundup - Day 4</strong>\r\n\r\n<strong>Panel: <em>Everything Eric Ries Has Learned Since 2011</em>, Eric Ries, Ted Greenwald</strong> Fans of <a href=\"http://theleanstartup.com/\">The Lean Startup</a> author, rejoice! Eric Ries announced a new book, crowd-sourced on Kickstarter, called <a href=\"http://www.fastcompany.com/3043745/most-creative-people/the-lean-startup-author-eric-ries-is-crowdsourcing-his-next-book-via-ki\">The Leader\'s Guide</a>. Don\'t be intimidated - just be entertained - by the number of special \'packages\' you can choose from - it\'s part of the gimmick! For reference, I went with the All-Access Package.\r\n\r\nQuick shout out to my new friends at Tech.co, Chute, Partnered, and General Assembly - great meeting you guys. Rock on, Austin, and see you in 2016!','Hello from Austin and another SXSW!','','inherit','open','open','','254-revision-v1','','','2015-03-18 20:07:44','2015-03-18 20:07:44','',254,'http://abbot-water.com/254-revision-v1/',0,'revision','',0),
	(260,1,'2015-03-19 15:21:10','2015-03-19 15:21:10','[vc_row gmbt_prlx_bg_type=\"parallax\" gmbt_prlx_break_parents=\"0\" gmbt_prlx_smooth_scrolling=\"\" gmbt_prlx_video_youtube_mute=\"\" gmbt_prlx_video_youtube_loop_trigger=\"0\" gmbt_prlx_video_aspect_ratio=\"16:9\" gmbt_prlx_parallax=\"none\" gmbt_prlx_speed=\"0.3\" gmbt_prlx_enable_mobile=\"\"][vc_column width=\"1/2\" el_class=\"bio-image\"][vc_single_image image=\"34\" alignment=\"center\" border_color=\"black\" img_link_large=\"\" img_link_target=\"_self\" img_size=\"500x667\" style=\"vc_box_border\"][/vc_column][vc_column width=\"1/2\"][themestudio_title title=\"Heather Bergstein\" align=\"align-center\" text_align=\"center\" title_color=\"#252525\" underline_color=\"#252525\"]President + Chief Strategist[/themestudio_title][vc_column_text]\r\n<p style=\"text-align: left;\">A results-driven digital brand marketing and media expert, Heather Bergstein has spent over a decade working with global Beauty and Fashion companies including L’Oreal, Ralph Lauren and Estee Lauder. Heather’s career began in traditional marketing, and that remains to be the foundation of her approach; she’s not a digital marketer, but a marketer with digital expertise.</p>\r\n<p style=\"text-align: left;\">As President and Chief Strategist of <strong>Abbot + Water</strong>, Heather works with brands, start-ups and publishers as a dot connector, cross-functional leader, and digital swat team of one, creating tailored and informed strategies that drive engagement and ROI, built to evolve in an ever-changing marketing landscape.</p>\r\n<p style=\"text-align: left;\">A passionate digital leader, Heather is a frequent panelist and industry participant with a focus on digital content, video and media strategy; her industry recognition speaks to her dedication. She is based in NYC, where she lives with her son, and bounces between NYC and Santa Monica (aka Silicon Beach), to stay on the pulse of media, tech and everything in between, coast to coast.</p>\r\n\r\n[/vc_column_text][/vc_column][/vc_row][vc_row][vc_column width=\"1/1\"][themestudio_title title=\"Industry Recognition + Membership\" align=\"align-center\" text_align=\"center\" title_color=\"#252525\" underline_color=\"#252525\"][/themestudio_title][vc_column_text]\r\n<ul class=\"recognition\">\r\n	<li>Brand Innovators 40 Under 40, Class of 2013</li>\r\n	<li>Editorial Board Member,<em> Journal of Business to Consumer Marketing</em></li>\r\n	<li>Internet Week 2014 Panelist, OMMA Social</li>\r\n	<li>Member, IAB MIXX Screening Committee, 2013 and 2014</li>\r\n	<li>Co-Founder, The Cabernet Group</li>\r\n	<li>Volunteer Content Contributor, Taste of Tribeca</li>\r\n	<li>Upcoming Panelist: Click Z Live NYC 2015</li>\r\n</ul>\r\n[/vc_column_text][/vc_column][/vc_row]','Bio + Credentials','','inherit','open','open','','8-revision-v1','','','2015-03-19 15:21:10','2015-03-19 15:21:10','',8,'http://abbot-water.com/8-revision-v1/',0,'revision','',0),
	(261,1,'2015-03-19 15:22:40','2015-03-19 15:22:40','[vc_row gmbt_prlx_bg_type=\"parallax\" gmbt_prlx_break_parents=\"0\" gmbt_prlx_smooth_scrolling=\"\" gmbt_prlx_video_youtube_mute=\"\" gmbt_prlx_video_youtube_loop_trigger=\"0\" gmbt_prlx_video_aspect_ratio=\"16:9\" gmbt_prlx_parallax=\"none\" gmbt_prlx_speed=\"0.3\" gmbt_prlx_enable_mobile=\"\"][vc_column width=\"1/2\" el_class=\"bio-image\"][vc_single_image image=\"34\" alignment=\"center\" border_color=\"black\" img_link_large=\"\" img_link_target=\"_self\" img_size=\"500x667\" style=\"vc_box_border\"][/vc_column][vc_column width=\"1/2\"][themestudio_title title=\"Heather Bergstein\" align=\"align-center\" text_align=\"center\" title_color=\"#252525\" underline_color=\"#252525\"]President + Chief Strategist[/themestudio_title][vc_column_text]\r\n<p style=\"text-align: left;\">A results-driven digital brand marketing and media expert, Heather Bergstein has spent over a decade working with global Beauty and Fashion companies including L’Oreal, Ralph Lauren and Estee Lauder. Heather’s career began in traditional marketing, and that remains to be the foundation of her approach; she’s not a digital marketer, but a marketer with digital expertise.</p>\r\n<p style=\"text-align: left;\">As President and Chief Strategist of <strong>Abbot + Water</strong>, Heather works with brands, start-ups and publishers as a dot connector, cross-functional leader, and digital swat team of one, creating tailored and informed strategies that drive engagement and ROI, built to evolve in an ever-changing marketing landscape.</p>\r\n<p style=\"text-align: left;\">A passionate digital leader, Heather is a frequent panelist and industry participant with a focus on digital content, video and media strategy; her industry recognition speaks to her dedication. She is based in NYC, where she lives with her son, and bounces between NYC and Santa Monica (aka Silicon Beach), to stay on the pulse of media, tech and everything in between, coast to coast.</p>\r\n\r\n[/vc_column_text][/vc_column][/vc_row][vc_row][vc_column width=\"1/1\" el_class=\"industry-rec\"][themestudio_title title=\"Industry Recognition + Membership\" align=\"align-center\" text_align=\"center\" title_color=\"#252525\" underline_color=\"#252525\"][/themestudio_title][vc_column_text]\r\n<ul class=\"recognition\">\r\n	<li>Brand Innovators 40 Under 40, Class of 2013</li>\r\n	<li>Editorial Board Member,<em> Journal of Business to Consumer Marketing</em></li>\r\n	<li>Internet Week 2014 Panelist, OMMA Social</li>\r\n	<li>Member, IAB MIXX Screening Committee, 2013 and 2014</li>\r\n	<li>Co-Founder, The Cabernet Group</li>\r\n	<li>Volunteer Content Contributor, Taste of Tribeca</li>\r\n	<li>Upcoming Panelist: Click Z Live NYC 2015</li>\r\n</ul>\r\n[/vc_column_text][/vc_column][/vc_row]','Bio + Credentials','','inherit','open','open','','8-revision-v1','','','2015-03-19 15:22:40','2015-03-19 15:22:40','',8,'http://abbot-water.com/8-revision-v1/',0,'revision','',0),
